- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses deep end-to-end training to teach the robot. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper involves teaching a robot to learn a task. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves a human teacher demonstrating the task via joystick.
